This refactored version:
1. Uses the actual battery capacity from the selected package when available
2. Falls back to the minimum capacity from availableBatteryPackages
3. Only shows ranges when we have the necessary data
4. Returns null values when we don't have enough information
5. Handles partial data better during loading states

